description:
Who changed the Sabbath, and why? Did God the father, Jesus, or the apostles change the Sabbath? If not, then who did it? Does man really have the authority to change God's law? 

In the Christian world today, there is much confusion about the true Bible Sabbath. Many sincere Christians have been deceived into accepting a false Sabbath that was never endorsed by the Bible. 

In this video, you will uncover one of history’s greatest deceptions. Hundreds of years ago, the Christian world was rocked by scandal. A blasphemous attempt was made to change God’s law. Amazingly, the Bible predicted this bombshell event. You will learn exactly who made the change, and their reason for doing it. You will also learn how you can prove your allegiance to God, in the face of this global deception. Hang onto your seat, and please pray for God's guidance before watching this life-changing video!
